		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="1) First node is triggered when DU has Accepted Bhaal and encounter the Jaheira+Minsc Confrontation. When combat begins with them, Some cultists will join the DU against them.&#xD;&#xA;2) Second node is when the Dark Urge dies in the duel, this AD plays and rest of combat NPC joins in to kill remaining companions.&#xD;&#xA;3) Thrid node happens when players broke the Duel.&#xD;&#xA;4) Fourth node triggers at the beginning of the duel." />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="5" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="In the Bhaal Temple, if players are Dark Urge, they have the opportunity to fight Orin one on one. Players are given a warning that if the companions jump in the battle, so does the rest of the temple." />
